p: In the District Court of the Third Judicial District of Washington Territory, Holding Terms at Seattle, in the County of King.
In the Matter of the Petition for writ of Habeas Corpus for the person of Nan Oy a Chinese woman
Here the reading and consideration of the matters set forth in the petition of Ah Ram for a writ of Habeas Corpus herein, it is considered by the Court that said writ be granted
